original_title: MTV Unplugged Presents: Miley Cyrus Backyard Sessions
overview: Miley Cyrus performs an acoustic set of original songs and covers including Britney Spears's "Gimme More," and is joined by Noah Cyrus for a rendition of "I Got So High That I Saw Jesus."
title: MTV Unplugged Presents: Miley Cyrus Backyard Sessions
